Package com.codeborne.selenide

@NullMarked @CheckReturnValue package com.codeborne.selenide
Public API of Selenide The most important classes are:
  1. com.codeborne.selenide.Selenide
  2. com.codeborne.selenide.Configuration
  3. com.codeborne.selenide.Selectors

You can start from this class: import static com.codeborne.selenide.Selenide.*;

Other classes will come automatically with a help of your IDE.
